suspension-warning.p1=We did this because we have suspended your agent code. We sent you a letter to confirm this.
suspension-warning.p2.single=This means you will not be able to use this service to ask for authorisation to {0}.
suspension-warning.p2.multi=This means you will not be able to use this service to ask clients for authorisation to:
suspension-warning.single.ITSA=send a client''s Income Tax updates through software
suspension-warning.multi.ITSA=send their Income Tax updates through software
